{"tid":2013186,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬來西亞封城2個月 百貨商場變身「養菌場」","createTime":"2020-05-12T06:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T06:58:41.000Z","uid":253829,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"70830601bb24809d94c4c3055e175a17fd6c65be","tid":2013186,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:48:51.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情影響下，馬來西亞政府也發布行動管制令，除了民生必需品的商店可以營業外，不少業者都暫停營業。大馬政府10日再次宣布管制令將延長4星期，好消息是，部分商家獲准重新開業，不過有民眾在購物中逛街時卻發現「宛如世界末日」的驚訝場景。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/k5M_BWR9jF5R0dOLsjXDHg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9Nzkz/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/ctwant_com_582/51d9e35cae6f4ee45c6aa0840f18a975\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fk5M_BWR9jF5R0dOLsjXDHg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9Nzkz%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fctwant_com_582%2F51d9e35cae6f4ee45c6aa0840f18a975&h=3b0e9149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有大馬網友在臉書粉專「沙巴新鲜事」PO照，表示在逛東馬沙巴的百貨商場時，赫然發現店內出售的不少皮製品似乎被蒙上一層砂，子細一看卻發現居然是發霉，包括不少皮鞋、皮包陳列品表面都鋪上一層又白又黃的霉菌，甚至有部分貨品似乎已遭霉菌侵蝕，畫面駭人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nA4YXGTY8MKrUlF1LOj1cQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9MzMy/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/ctwant_com_582/0e9e136d1c48b72e721282d266d0da3f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnA4YXGTY8MKrUlF1LOj1cQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9MzMy%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fctwant_com_582%2F0e9e136d1c48b72e721282d266d0da3f&h=2a9b8204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了陳列品、皮帶、皮包和皮鞋等等，就連商場內的皮製座椅也可看見霉菌滋生，似乎只要是皮製品就無法倖免。原PO表示，由於大馬多間百貨公司暫停營業近2個月，百貨公司可能在管制令期間無人打理，加上冷氣關閉導致室內升溫加上空氣不流通，有利於細菌滋生，皮製用品自然成為霉菌溫床。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GiJ7IrSLjNyH6x.TG1wQtQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9ODQw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/ctwant_com_582/c8ad18a157b1718595ab3d5591cfd115\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGiJ7IrSLjNyH6x.TG1wQtQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9ODQw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fctwant_com_582%2Fc8ad18a157b1718595ab3d5591cfd115&h=16d7ea03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有部分網友指出，其實百貨公司的陳列品都有不少逛街的民眾會觸摸，因此含菌量較高，加上業者在管制令前夕並未有妥善清潔動作，經過2個月的時間，發霉情況是預料中事。另外還有網友表示，這個情況正好測試產品是否為真皮，發霉情況若不嚴重，或是未發霉的產品，有可能是合成物料製成，並非真皮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Zd7jtp67u08A4KkUDfSvFg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9ODQw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/ctwant_com_582/d4f46d4c20bfe030bf94be219568dec0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZd7jtp67u08A4KkUDfSvFg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9ODQw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fctwant_com_582%2Fd4f46d4c20bfe030bf94be219568dec0&h=f060cd52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9E%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E2%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E7%99%BE%E8%B2%A8%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E8%AE%8A%E8%BA%AB-%E9%A4%8A%E8%8F%8C%E5%A0%B4-131301850.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25BA%259E%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%259F%258E2%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%25BA%25AB-%25E9%25A4%258A%25E8%258F%258C%25E5%25A0%25B4-131301850.html&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmK2paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=dbd12500\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9E%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E2%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E7%99%BE%E8%B2%A8%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E8%AE%8A%E8%BA%AB-%E9%A4%8A%E8%8F%8C%E5%A0%B4-131301850.html</a>"},{"pid":"e0ea4f88ffd0436be96fb039d12304c97e3c7da8","tid":2013186,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:51:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cceae13be4eab66